sentences.en: The kids were jammed like canned sardines.

sentences.en: A small pebble had jammed the pump.

sentences.en: Protesting viewers jammed the BBC switchboard.

sentences.vi: Anh ta đút mạnh chìa vào ổ khóa.

sentences.en: Her scream stopped jammed in her throat.

sentences.en: This country's cram-jammed with game.
